-- Cencosud Taps Santander, Larrain Vial for Chile Sale, DF Says
-- B y   S e b a s t i a n   B o y d
-- 2012-05-11T12:37:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-11/cencosud-taps-santander-larrain-vial-for-chile-sale-df-says.html
Cencosud SA (CENCOSUD) , Chile’s biggest retailer
by sales, hired Larrain Vial SA and a unit of Banco Santander SA
to manage the local leg of a share sale, Diario Financiero
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Cencosud plans to sell as much as $2 billion of new shares
in Chile and  New York  at the end of the second quarter, the
Santiago-based newspaper reported, citing people familiar with
the transaction that it didn’t name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sebastian Boyd in Santiago at 
 sboyd9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  